query:
SELECT 
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM supplierCoverageCountries WHERE supplierId = 12) as countryCount,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM supplierPriorityCities WHERE supplierId = 12) as cityCount,
  ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM supplierCoverageCountries WHERE supplierId = 12) + 
   (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM supplierPriorityCities WHERE supplierId = 12)) * 3 * 5 as virtualMatrixSize
